| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1809 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 828eb5ec-cae6-58fe-941d-7aff6aa239a0"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
